        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "UNIVERSAL FIT MENS BELT: One size fits all; 52 inches in total length; extra length can be tucked within belt loops or cut to fit while singeing the ends; very adjustable and comfortable; no pre-made belt holes, just stick the belt clasp through the paracord weave wherever it fits most comfortably for best fit",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "PARACORD BELT SPECIFICATIONS: Unraveled Total Length: 110 feet; Belt Waist Length: 52 inches; Belt Width: 1.5 inches; Stainless Steel Belt Buckle; Color: Black Paracord Belt",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "THE ULTIMATE EDC SURVIVAL BELT: Unravel the paracord braided weave to provide a rope source of strong survival cord at your disposal to craft a weapon, build a stretcher, fish for food, build a shelter and much more",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "FASHIONABLE DESIGN: While being highly dependable and extremely versatile this piece of survival gear can be worn everyday for when the most unexpected situations may arise",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "EASY TO MAINTAIN: Fully washable, easy to clean; wash, rinse and repeat; can be run through the washing machine and air dried",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
